main event: Mrs. Laura Warren reported a sighting of a luminous, disk-shaped object moving at a high speed over Warren, Minnesota in March 1967.
interesting points: The object was observed at an altitude of approximately 3000 feet,The sighting lasted for 15 minutes,Observations were made directly by a single witness,The weather was clear with no clouds at the time of the sighting,The report was filed under Project Blue Book.
witness description: Mrs. Laura Warren, a resident of Warren, Minnesota
